Well, what's the point if you've got no one to share it with?

130
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:47,640
你又太直白了
There's that bluntness again.

131
00:05:47,670 --> 00:05:49,800
生命中有没有那么一刻
Has there ever been a time in your life

132
