you know how to cut through red tape.

144
00:06:26,010 --> 00:06:27,640
如果有人能钻政策的空子
And if anyone can work the system

145
00:06:27,640 --> 00:06:30,930
帮我领养个孩子  那人就是你
and find me a baby, it's you.

146
